{
  "uid": "eigen-loki-logs-v1",
  "title": "Eigen Logs — Loki Overview",
  "tags": [
    "eigen",
    "loki",
    "logs",
    "observability"
  ],
  "timezone": "browser",
  "schemaVersion": 39,
  "version": 1,
  "refresh": "30s",
  "time": {
    "from": "now-6h",
    "to": "now"
  },
  "editable": true,
  "fiscalYearStartMonth": 0,
  "templating": {
    "list": [
      {
        "name": "service",
        "label": "Service",
        "type": "query",
        "datasource": {
          "type": "loki",
          "uid": "DS_LOKI"
        },
        "query": "label_values({container=~\"eigen-.*\"}, compose_service)",
        "definition": "label_values({container=~\"eigen-.*\"}, compose_service)",
        "refresh": 2,
        "sort": 1,
        "multi": true,
        "includeAll": true,
        "allValue": ".*",
        "current": {
          "selected": true,
          "text": "All",
          "value": "$__all"
        }
      },
      {
        "name": "level",
        "label": "Level",
        "type": "custom",
        "query": "trace,debug,info,warn,error,fatal",
        "multi": true,
        "includeAll": true,
        "allValue": ".*",
        "current": {
          "selected": true,
          "text": "All",
          "value": "$__all"
        }
      }
    ]
  },
  "annotations": {
    "list": [
      {
        "builtIn": 1,
        "datasource": {
          "type": "grafana",
          "uid": "-- Grafana --"
        },
        "enable": true,
        "hide": true,
        "iconColor": "rgba(0, 211, 255, 1)",
        "name": "Annotations & Alerts",
        "type": "dashboard"
      }
    ]
  },
  "panels": [
    {
      "type": "text",
      "title": "How to use this dashboard",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 7,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 0
      },
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "### Ready-to-use LogQL snippets\n\n- All logs: `{container=~\"eigen-.*\"}`\n- Selected services: `{container=~\"eigen-.*\", compose_service=~\"$service\"}`\n- Errors and warnings: `{container=~\"eigen-.*\", compose_service=~\"$service\"} |~ \"(?i)warn|error|fatal\"`\n- Single service: `{container=~\"eigen-.*\", compose_service=\"system-api\"}`\n\n### Services covered\n\n`system-api`, `eigen-kernel`, `eigen-compiler`, `driver-manager`, `eigen-neuro-symbolic-service`,\n`benchmark-service`, `observability-metrics`, `loki`, `tempo`, `prometheus`, `grafana`,\n`promtail`, `minio`, `minio-init`, `loki-landing`, `tempo-landing`, `otel-collector`\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Log volume by service",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 8,
        "w": 12,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 7
      },
      "datasource": {
        "type": "loki",
        "uid": "DS_LOKI"
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "sum by (compose_service) (count_over_time({container=~\"eigen-.*\", compose_service=~\"$service\"}[5m]))",
          "legendFormat": "{{compose_service}}"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "logs"
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "timeFrom": "24h"
    },
    {
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Errors and warnings by service",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 8,
        "w": 12,
        "x": 12,
        "y": 7
      },
      "datasource": {
        "type": "loki",
        "uid": "DS_LOKI"
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "{container=~\"eigen-.*\", compose_service=~\"$service\"} |~ \"(?i)warn|error|fatal\"",
          "legendFormat": "{{compose_service}}"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "logs"
        },
        "overrides": []
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "table",
      "title": "Top noisy services (15m)",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 10,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 15
      },
      "datasource": {
        "type": "loki",
        "uid": "DS_LOKI"
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "topk(10, sum by (compose_service) (count_over_time({container=~\"eigen-.*\"}[15m])))",
          "legendFormat": "{{compose_service}}"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "logs"
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "timeFrom": "24h"
    },
    {
      "type": "logs",
      "title": "Live logs for selected service(s)",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 14,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 25
      },
      "datasource": {
        "type": "loki",
        "uid": "DS_LOKI"
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "{container=~\"eigen-.*\", compose_service=~\"$service\"}",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {},
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": {
        "showLabels": true,
        "showTime": true,
        "wrapLogMessage": true,
        "prettifyLogMessage": false,
        "sortOrder": "Descending"
      },
      "timeFrom": "24h"
    }
  ]
}
